[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 1.4"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 1.4 are now fixed in
Tails 1.4.1.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to
Tails 1.4.1|news/version_1.4.1]] as soon as possible.

